snippet.title: Willy Wombat - Early development footage
snippet.description:
Really neat early look at the game Willy Wombat for the Sega Saturn and some of the early pre-rendered character models.
The video this clip is from was made sometime in 1996 and says Willy Wombat was to be due out "next year in January" but this was not the case; it ended up coming out August 27th, 1997.
Footage from here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2UYDl8SSrlQ
